# Keep the build context free of artifacts that must never land in an
# image.  The packaging Containerfile uses explicit `COPY` paths, so
# this mainly stops `COPY docs/` from sweeping in design sources.
#
# Do NOT exclude target/: tests/integration/Containerfile copies the
# prebuilt binary and examples from target/release/ (repo-root build
# context), and a root .containerignore applies to every build here.

# VCS metadata.
.git/
.gitignore

# GIMP design sources -- only the rendered PNGs are served.
**/*.xcf

# Editor scratch files.
*.swp
